/ol></div></div>\t\n\t\t<figure><img width=\"300\" height=\"300\" src=\"https://static.dezeen.com/uploads/2025/11/rosa-maria-house-delavegacanolassorosa-maria-house-delavegacanolasso-madrid-spain-architecture_dezeen_2364_sq-300x300.jpg\" class=\"attachment-medium size-medium\" alt=\"Rosa María House by Delavegacanolasso\" decoding=\"async\" data-pin-nopin=\"1\" srcset=\"https://static.dezeen.com/uploads/2025/11/rosa-maria-house-delavegacanolassorosa-maria-house-delavegacanolasso-madrid-spain-architecture_dezeen_2364_sq-300x300.jpg 1x, https://static.dezeen.com/uploads/2025/11/rosa-maria-house-delavegacanolassorosa-maria-house-delavegacanolasso-madrid-spain-architecture_dezeen_2364_sq-600x600.jpg 2x\" /></figure>\n\t<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2026/02/21/the-willow-play-cafe-toronto-denizens-of-design-ds-studio/\">\n\t\t<figure><img width=\"300\" height=\"300\" src=\"https://static.dezeen.com/uploads/2026/02/imgi_1_the-willow_denizens_dezeen_sq1-300x300.jpg\" class=\"attachment-medium size-medium\" alt=\"Denizens of Design\" decoding=\"async\" data-pin-nopin=\"1\" srcset=\"https://static.dezeen.com/uploads/2026/02/imgi_1_the-willow_denizens_dezeen_sq1-300x300.jpg 1x, https://static.dezeen.com/uploads/2026/02/imgi_1_the-willow_denizens_dezeen_sq1-600x600.jpg 2x\" /></figure>\n\t\t<h3>\"It's time to bring new Mexican architecture to the table\" says Lanza Atelier</h3>\n\t\t<figure><img width=\"300\" height=\"300\" src=\"https://static.dezeen.com/uploads/2026/01/a-serpentine-pavilion-lanza-atelier-london-architecture-uk-news_dezeen_2364_portrait_sq-300x300.jpg\" class=\"attachment-medium size-medium\" alt=\"Lanza Atelier portrait\" decoding=\"async\" data-pin-nopin=\"1\" srcset=\"https://static.dezeen.com/uploads/2026/01/a-serpentine-pavilion-lanza-atelier-london-architecture-uk-news_dezeen_2364_portrait_sq-300x300.jpg 1x, https://static.dezeen.com/uploads/2026/01/a-serpentine-pavilion-lanza-atelier-london-architecture-uk-news_dezeen_2364_portrait_sq-600x600.jpg 2x\" /></figure>\n\t<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2026/02/14/oddly-satisfying-architecture-roundups/\">\n\t\t<h3>Ten examples of oddly satisfying architecture</h3>\n</ul><ul id=\"menu-footer-menu-3\" class=\"menu\"><li id=\"menu-item-987251\" class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-taxonomy menu-item-object-category menu-item-987251\"><a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/architecture/\" class=\"nav-link\">Architecture</a></li>\n<li id=\"menu-item-987252\" class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-taxonomy menu-item-object-category menu-item-987252\"><a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/design/\" class=\"nav-link\">Design</a></li>","cwd":"/home/node/.openclaw/workspace/researcher"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772945517342}}
